properties.areaDesc: 5NM East of a line from Fairport MI to Rock Island Passage; Green Bay North of line from Cedar River MI to Rock Island Passage; Seul Choix Point to Point Detour MI
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 10 at 4:34PM EST until January 12 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 40 kt and
waves 3 to 6 feet expected.

* WHERE...Green Bay North of line from Cedar River MI to Rock
Island Passage, Seul Choix Point to Point Detour MI and 5NM
East of a line from Fairport MI to Rock Island Passage.

* WHEN...From 1 AM Saturday to 4 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 1 AM SATURDAY TO 4 AM EST SUNDAY
